snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: The Modern Zombie Taxi Co. | PS VR
snippet.description: The Zombie Apocalypse is over. The zombies won. Now they want to go about their deaths like normal people. They are the Modern Zombies, and you are their taxi driver.
